{"type":"message","id":"40ee5b2a","parentId":"d0f79b32","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:59:55.611Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about my skill, workspace, and agent. This seems like they want to understand the setup or configuration. Let me provide a concise overview of what's in this workspace.\n\nFrom what I've read:\n- This is the wechat-assistant workspace\n- I'm running as agent \"wechat-assistant\"\n- There are some skills available but I should check what's actually installed\n\nThe user might want to know:\n1. What skills I have access to\n2. What workspace I'm in\n3. What agent configuration I'm running\n\nLet me provide a helpful summary without being too verbose.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"I'm running as agent `wechat-assistant` in workspace `/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-wechat-assistant`.\n\n**Available skills:**\n- `agent-reach` — search/read 14 platforms (Twitter, Reddit, YouTube, B站, 小红书, 抖音, etc.)\n- `feishu-doc`, `feishu-drive`, `feishu-perm`, `feishu-wiki` — Feishu operations\n- `weather` — forecasts via wttr.in/Open-Meteo\n- `clawhub` — skill management\n- `coding-agent` — delegate to Codex/Claude Code/Pi\n- `skill-creator` — author/edit skills\n- `healthcheck`, `node-connect` — diagnostics\n\n**Workspace files:**\n- `SOUL.md` — personality guidelines\n- `USER.md` — empty (learning about you)\n- `MEMORY.md` — long-term memory (Aliyun image gen key stored)\n- `IDENTITY.md` — empty (no name/persona set yet)\n\nWhat do you want to do? Set up my identity, work on something specific, or explore what's possible?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1350,"output":364,"cacheRead":8704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10418,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773932383697}}
