{"type":"message","id":"2a76e77b","parentId":"7e31a246","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:11:57.722Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check if the directory exists and list its contents. Actually, I should just explain how skill loading works in OpenClaw. \n\nIn OpenClaw, skills can be loaded from multiple sources:\n1. Built-in skills in `/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/`\n2. User skills in `~/.openclaw/skills/`\n3. Workspace-specific skills in the workspace's `skills/` folder\n\nTo load skills from the workspace's `skills/` directory, the user needs to:\n1. Create a skill folder with a `SKILL.md` file\n2. The skill should be automatically discovered if it's properly structured\n\nLet me provide a clear answer to the user.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw 会自动从以下几个地方加载 skills：\n\n1. **系统 skills**: `/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/`\n2. **用户 skills**: `~/.openclaw/skills/`\n3. **Workspace skills**: `workspace/skills/` ← 你现在在这里\n\n**要让 workspace 里的技能生效：**\n\n1. 确保技能目录结构正确：\n   ```\n   workspace-wechat-assistant/skills/\n   └── your-skill/\n       ├── SKILL.md          # 必需\n       └── (其他脚本文件)\n   ```\n\n2. 每个 skill 需要一个 `SKILL.md` 文件来描述它的功能\n\n3. **重新加载** — 修改后需要重启 agent 或新开 session 才能识别\n\n你想创建新 skill，还是把已有的 skill 移到这个 workspace？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":237,"output":315,"cacheRead":11520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12072,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773933108384}}
